Dear friends, Happy Saturday!
The weather wasn't great last week, so we flew again today.
There was power-on stall recovery, power-off stall recovery, slow flight, simulated engine failure (!), route training, three landings with the instructor's help, and one go-around.
Everything is good ^_^
